headline: NIKE, Inc. Announces Second Quarter Fiscal 2025 Earnings and Conference Call
summary: BEAVERTON, Ore., November 21, 2024--NIKE, Inc. (NYSE: NKE) plans to release its second quarter fiscal 2025 financial results on Thursday, December 19, 2024, at approximately 1:15 p.m. PT, following the close of regular stock market trading hours. Following the news release, NIKE, Inc. management will host a conference call beginning at 2:00 p.m. PT to review results.

headline: Bill Ackman Is Piling Into Nike Stock: 3 Things Investors Need to Know
summary: In its latest quarterly report, management didn't provide any guidance.  Nike is operating in a competitive environment, and rivals like Lululemon and On Holding have captured market share from it in recent years.  Long-term investors might want to follow Ackman into a Nike position, but don't make it a large one, and don't expect it to reward you overnight.

summary: The Dow Jones Industrial Average (DJINDICES: ^DJI) is enjoying a nice year.  The venerable stock market index has risen more than 15%, putting it on track to beat its 2023 return of nearly 14%.  Several top-performing stocks have contributed to the Dow Jones rally.
